For those who do not wish to read the entire changelog, the two important changes are these:<p><pre><code>    Subroutine Signatures

    sub foo ($left, $right) {
        return $left + $right;
    }
</code></pre>
<a href="https://metacpan.org/pod/release/RJBS/perl-5.20.0/pod/perlsub.pod#Signatures" rel="nofollow">https://metacpan.org/pod/release/RJBS/perl-5.20.0/pod/perlsu...</a><p><pre><code>    Postfix dereferencing

    $array_ref->@*;
</code></pre>
instead of<p><pre><code>    @{$array_ref};
</code></pre>
<a href="https://metacpan.org/pod/release/RJBS/perl-5.20.0/pod/perldelta.pod#Experimental-Postfix-Dereferencing" rel="nofollow">https://metacpan.org/pod/release/RJBS/perl-5.20.0/pod/perlde...</a>
